{"id":"23033","name":"忍法帖•繚亂破魔","rarity":5,"path":"Mage","desc":"「忍界」某地，灰慘的陰霾籠罩著城市。\n「咿呀——！」\n少女的身影在怪物之中穿行，其殘影如同絢麗的色彩揮灑於沒有月光的大地。\n煙塵之中，「邪忍」們痛苦呻吟，驚疑不定。\n「你……是誰……」\n「在下忍號『亂破』，一心不亂，破邪顯正是也。」\n「邪忍」們面面相覷，意欲四處逃竄。\n「閣下，準備好唸誦辭世句了嗎——」\n手裡劍如流光旋轉，危險的氣息席捲而來。\n「奧義•繚亂滅破殺陣！」\n身後的爆炸照亮了滿目瘡痍的夜晚。\n她深吸一口氣，躍入如重金屬般喧囂的霓虹燈光之中。\n「此等邪祟，實際醜惡。繚亂忍俠的壯絕•狩獵，仍需繼續……」","icon":"icon/light_cone/23033.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/23033.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/23033.png","ranks":{"id":"23033","skill":"除邪","desc":"使裝備者的擊破特攻提高#1[i]%。進入戰鬥時立即恢復#2[f1]點能量，且裝備者施放終結技後獲得【雷遁】，發動2次普通攻擊後，裝備者行動提前#3[i]%，並移除【雷遁】。裝備者施放終結技後會重置【雷遁】。","params":[[0.6,30,0.5],[0.7,32.5,0.55],[0.8,35,0.6],[0.9,37.5,0.65],[1,40,0.7]],"properties":[[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.6}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.7}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.8}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.9}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":1}]]},"promotions":{"id":"23033","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":26.4,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":24,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":58.08,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":100.32,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":142.56,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":184.8,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":168,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":227.04,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":269.28,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":5000},{"id":"114001","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":10000},{"id":"110201","num":4},{"id":"114001","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":20000},{"id":"110202","num":4},{"id":"114002","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":50000},{"id":"110202","num":8},{"id":"114002","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":100000}